hybridization_protocol: Following fragmentation, 10 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 450.
scanner_type: GeneChips were scanned using the GeneChip Scanner 3000 7G.
data_processing: Expression levels of 17,527 genes were extracted from Affymetrix HU133 Plus 2.0 arrays using updated array annotation (Dai et al., 2005) based on reorganizing probes to gene specific probe sets, excluding inaccurate or wrongly annotated probes.
